626
00:47:35.958 --> 00:47:36.788
l'm a teacher.

627
00:47:36.859 --> 00:47:38.019
lt's my job to know.

628
00:47:38.261 --> 00:47:38.852
Shall we start?

629
00:47:38.928 --> 00:47:39.952
