it's all right.

651
00:49:34.510 --> 00:49:35.534
You need to surrender.

652
00:49:35.645 --> 00:49:36.475
Stop!

653
00:49:36.512 --> 00:49:37.501
You need to surrender.

654
00:49:37.580 --> 00:49:38.478
Stop it!

655
00:49:38.547 --> 00:49:39.571
