for one more student?

725
00:54:10.386 --> 00:54:11.512
Look at him...

726
00:54:11.587 --> 00:54:12.918
Forget it D...

727
00:54:27.736 --> 00:54:29.761
Rhea. this is Gopi!

728
00:54:29.872 --> 00:54:32.602
Gopi sir. l've heard
a lot about you.

729
00:54:32.675 --> 00:54:34.267
Sir...

730
00:54:34.343 --> 00:54:37.278
